                                    a.post-tag.round-xl.small General
                                    a.post-tag.round-xl.small Media
                                a.badge.fa-comments.text-uppercase.font-secondary 13 comments
                            a(href="blog_post.html").btn-link Read More

                //End slider

                = '\n'
                //Start quote

                .col-xs-12.section-border
                    article.well
                        blockquote.quote
                            p.
                                Design is the fundamental soul of a man-made creation that ends up expressing itself in successive outer layers of the product or service. The iMac is not just the color or translucence or the shape of the shell. The essence of the iMac is to be the finest possible consumer computer in which each element plays together.
                            footer
                                cite(title="Source Title") Steve Jobs

                        .blog-info
                            .pull-md-left
                                time(datetime="2015").meta.fa-calendar Feb 10, 2014
                                a.badge.fa-user.text-uppercase.font-secondary Admin
